data.description: This magnificent property built in 2019 boasts 4 bedrooms, a bonus room, loft, 2 full baths, a half bath, and a 2-car garage located in a cul-de-sac in the highly favored community of Hidden River.  This immaculate home offers all of the bells and whistles.  Step inside the exquisite foyer and you will be greeted with style & beauty around every corner.  You will be impressed with the spacious living room which is great for endless hours of entertaining.  The super-sized open island style kitchen is accommodated with all black appliances and beautiful counter tops.  This immaculate kitchen will bring out the gourmet cook in you.  The colossal bonus room has tile flooring and located at the from right wing of the property.  Take the stairs and relax in the massive loft upstairs.  The pool table is perfect for family gatherings and will convey with the property.  Grace yourself in the impeccable main master suite which is gorgeously designed and complimented by dual sinks, oversized shower and a custom-built shelving in the walk-in closet.  The additional bedrooms are all enormous in size.  The laundry closet is centrally located upstairs, and the washer and dryer will convey.  You will fall in love with the gigantic size back yard and no rear neighbors.  This subdivision is centrally located in the heart of Zephyrhills and surrounded by tons of shopping, dining and major roads for commuting.  Don't miss this opportunity of a lifetime to make this home yours.  Request a showing today, you won't be disappointed.
